Additionally Wizards published a series of Free Online Adventures on their website from 2000 to 2005. This is the complete list of adventures, with links to the original presentation articles. Fortunately some of the files related to those adventures are preserved via archive.com (replace the "archive" in the url with www and select "search archived web sites") side and the remaining files can be found dmguild.com.
